Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:39.78,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}are naught but a trivial matter to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.78,0:01:45.00,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}Although I'm caught in the past and I bewail the future
