Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:08.98,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}The finite is indicated by two hands of a clock
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.98,0:02:13.23,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}As I inch ever closer towards the cruelly contracted choice
