Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:22.78,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}That drives my will to go beyond the World Lines
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.78,0:02:27.79,op trans,,0,0,0,,{}in order to preserve that smile of yours
