Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.33,0:00:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.48,0:00:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.84,0:00:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel her. She's really here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.54,0:00:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a spirit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to call the cops?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.56,0:00:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I just want to know the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were stabbed right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.47,0:00:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by "the truth"?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.05,0:00:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you stupid? Do you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.80,0:00:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Louise's famous line!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.60,0:00:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.27,0:00:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You were stabbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.25,0:00:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hours ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.48,0:00:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,during Doctor Nakabachi's press conference at Radio Kaikan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.28,0:00:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin, try to control your delusions.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.90,0:00:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Nakabachi's press conference was canceled!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.11,0:00:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Makise! It's almost time!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:01.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.20,0:01:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Are you running away?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.64,0:01:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.35,0:01:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Hououin...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.29,0:01:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.69,0:02:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to start off by thanking you all for coming here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much experience with lectures like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.36,0:03:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,so I hope you'll bear with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.16,0:03:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise Kurisu's giving the lecture...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.91,0:03:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So she isn't a spirit, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Still bringing that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been asked to speak to you about time machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a little different from what I talked about in my {\i1}Science Magazine{\i0} essay,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'd like to give it a try.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Time machines?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I should just start off by saying that I think time machines are nothing more than a pipe dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.14,0:03:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to spend this lecture discussing how I arrived at that conclusio—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.44,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Objection!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Time machines are an impossibility?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's far too early to conclude that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.03,0:03:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin, you're embarrassing yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think that timing has anything to do with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's theoretically impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.67,0:04:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's change the format of this lecture to a discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.01,0:04:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that will make it a little easier for the more stubborn people to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Mr. Hououin Kyouma?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise Kurisu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And from this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.53,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,we can conclude that, in a universe based on string theory,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.87,0:04:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,time travel is completely unrealistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hououin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.04,0:04:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I imagine so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why not find some exotic matter for us,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.80,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hououin?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I have to say. But if you have any further objections, I'm listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.01,0:04:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Hououin.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so damned arrogant,\N just because you've a little bit of genius!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... She must be an agent of The Organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.65,0:04:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It's hot... It's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.69,0:05:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The lecture was, in and of itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,an act of carefully planned psychological warfare, aimed at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not buying it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Eight...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.04,0:05:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nine...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more swing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.80,0:05:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Ruka!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.68,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.14,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Mr. Okabe... No, Mr. Kyouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot the secret words, Rukako.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,E-El Psy... Congre...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.44,0:05:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Congroo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.61,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what did you want me to carry?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.99,0:05:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.45,0:05:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayushii can't carry all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.70,0:05:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad brought them, but there's too much for just us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.59,0:06:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for donating these provisions to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.50,0:06:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This will raise morale amongst the lab members.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.46,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad you like them...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruka practices swinging a sword daily!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.02,0:06:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I promised Oka... I mean, Mr. Kyouma.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.85,0:06:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,When the "Magical Blade Samidare" acknowledges you as a suitable wielder,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,it will unleash the hidden power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.99,0:06:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You got such a deal on it at the weapons store... Only 980 yen!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, show me the results of your training.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you attempt an exorcism?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.42,0:06:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I suppose... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.04,0:06:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you need a real exorcism, you should talk to my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.47,0:06:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,An evil spirit has possessed my right hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and perform the exorcism, before it consumes my entire body!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:55.97,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.39,0:06:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a different hand than last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The evil spirit possessed this one today, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.23,0:07:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Urushibara Ruka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The mannerisms and voice of a woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.49,0:07:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No... More feminine than any woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.53,0:07:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Taller than Mayuri, but so very thin...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks great in a shrine maiden outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But he's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.46,0:07:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it's so hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The cicadas are crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.55,0:07:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.60,0:07:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.64,0:07:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruka's so great, being able to do those exorcisms!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's the scion of a shrine clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's off-limits?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.12,0:07:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this leads behind the Radio Kaikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Radio Kaikan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me those.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.88,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to get to work soon, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.60,0:08:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm working late tonight, so I'll be going straight home afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Mayuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You truly didn't hear a scream, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.24,0:08:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A scream? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, at Radio Kaikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.49,0:08:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.37,0:08:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.08,0:08:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Okarin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, nobody remembers...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.05,0:08:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Daru.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.47,0:08:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Not Makise Kurisu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're closing early today, Mr. Braun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you not to call me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm interviewing a part-timer today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:12.57,Default,,0,0,0,,A part-timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A dreary, declining shop run by
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,an over-muscled old man needs a part-timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.07,0:09:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.58,0:09:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,'Sup!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.37,0:09:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that was the popular way to say "hi" now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't possibly be your part-timer...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.13,0:09:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.09,0:09:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Amane Suzuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.26,0:09:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Age?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Reason for working here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.47,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I love CRT TVs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.89,0:09:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're hired!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.35,0:09:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a comedy routine?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.10,0:09:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,His name's Okabe.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He's an oaf who rents a room upstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Okabe! It's Hououin—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it! I'll double your rent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Okabe Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.53,0:09:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, what's in those bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.82,0:09:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Special intelligence corn that was donated to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.66,0:10:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want some, you must appropriately compensate—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.83,0:10:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Corn?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.45,Default,,0,0,0,,With the little bumps?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.45,0:10:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is how it looks when it's fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.41,0:10:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I see—?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.16,0:10:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.83,0:10:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Organization has targeted many people
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.79,0:10:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,for coming into contact with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sara, Claudia, Simone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.26,0:10:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want, we could talk about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.68,0:10:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about him. He's just spouting crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Think what you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Someday, the entire world will be in the palm of my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So, that's what's popular these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.84,0:10:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Crashed around 12:00...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Mayuri and Daru were right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.60,0:11:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The conference was canceled?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.23,0:11:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise Kurisu stabbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.69,0:11:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that some kind of hallucination?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}@channel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,John Titor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.18,0:11:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,SERN has a monopoly on time machines.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No ordinary person, nor nation, nor business can acquire one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,They've only used them for their own self interests,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,bringing the world into a dystopia.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to fulfill the noble mission of changing my present.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I came here to destroy the dystopia SERN has built, and once again obtain our freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you claim that SERN dictates the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're talking about the so called Grandfather Paradox, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's been disproven.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's possible to meet yourself in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do, you simply move world lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me begin by saying
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.67,0:12:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,that time isn't a single line, moving from the past to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.18,0:12:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,It's comprised of an infinite number of parallel lines, like rivers, called "world lines."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.27,0:12:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For example, let's say a serial killer was to murder you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I came from the future and prevented it,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the world would diverge into two lines:
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.69,0:12:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,a world in which you had survived\N and a world in which you had died.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,So, this Titor is Japanese, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.95,0:12:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,A self-proclaimed time traveler,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,who appeared on the American Internet, in the year 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:13:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He claimed to have come from the year 2036 in order to save the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.67,0:13:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He then became famous on the Internet, and several books were eventually published about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But I didn't think I'd see some idiot pretending to be Titor {\i1}now{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's click this link and read up on Titor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru must've deleted the link on Titor...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:27.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Twelve?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.41,0:13:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it was ten years ago, but it was huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.16,0:13:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not here! What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.29,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a book collection on him, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.51,0:13:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.26,0:13:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.89,0:13:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at Faris'—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to the books?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.39,0:13:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The books?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.93,0:13:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The books on John Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a bunch of them on the bookshelf, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.65,0:14:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd they all go?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Okarin?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.90,0:14:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's... John Titor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I stayed up most of the night looking into John Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I found every bit of information on the Internet that I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.62,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(100,900,\1c&HFFFFFF&\2c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I want an answer from Titor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,About ten years ago... In other words, the year 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.01,0:14:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's interesting that you should ask that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But unfortunately, I've never been to the year 2000.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Nor do I intend to go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.20,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You there! You! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You took my picture, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:15:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You should delete it! For your own sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.58,0:15:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.04,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if I've made you unhappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.21,0:15:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you taking pictures of?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.88,0:15:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:19.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(5237,7155,\1c&HFFFFFF&\2c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Of where I walked today... Of what I saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.19,0:15:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to ask you about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a retro PC.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you recognize it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.49,0:15:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anyone who might?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Daru, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.87,0:15:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.54,0:15:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Delete that photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.79,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The e-mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,For that person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:15:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Are you threatening me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,If you tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.93,0:15:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll delete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.27,0:16:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,But I won't sell out my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.32,0:16:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give you my own e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:11.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It says "Hououin Kyouma" right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Just send me a blank mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.00,0:16:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send something back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.14,0:16:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Okarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.39,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.85,0:16:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,When I'm working, it's Mayushii NyanNyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, "Okarin" kind of sounds like "Welcome."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.28,0:16:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Daru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyouma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.53,0:16:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've missed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.20,0:17:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to visiting every three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Organization's sabotage has been just awful...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The Organization's gone that far?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.63,0:17:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you'll hold another secret meeting today to decide how to defeat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.34,0:17:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the usual Stealth Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,On it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd let me join in!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.59,0:17:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Organization is far too vast for you to handle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I've got my forbidden special move...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You finally mastered it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.14,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,After overcoming months of harsh training in the Highlands of Guiana
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and the death of my master, at last I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've mastered it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never forgive you. Ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.33,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So, about what I said in my mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.54,0:17:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe talking to a winner makes me a loser.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've no interest in that girl and her lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this today's "you're the last one I want to hear that from" thread?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.13,0:17:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, cheater!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:17:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Your 2D wives are crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.51,0:17:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Faris is special!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.89,0:18:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She may be 3D, but she has a 2D soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, look at this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.77,0:18:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an IBN 5100, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,IBN?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.02,0:18:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A legendary retro PC.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was about a month ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard a rumor that there was one somewhere in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She must've heard about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.91,0:18:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.49,0:18:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,No one ever found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.24,0:18:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the famous "Lightning Fast Neithardt" could find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.29,0:18:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means it probably never existed in the first place, and that's my final answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that valuable?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It was sold over thirty years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, nobody bought PCs. They were too expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.64,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how stuff ends up incredibly rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.22,0:18:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent that mail...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.73,0:18:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Kiryuu Moeka...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:56.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Age 20... No real job... \NI'm sending it, whether you like it or not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:19:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the same girl I just talked to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.28,0:19:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.16,0:19:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Be glad I didn't sell you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rare and valuable PC,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.37,0:19:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's a good chance it's not in Akihabara.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,El Psy Congroo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.00,0:19:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Nyan Nyan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my "The World is in Danger" omelet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yummy...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.43,0:19:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:27.89,SignJ,,0,0,0,,The World is in Danger!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.39,0:19:33.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The analysis conducted by the university laboratory
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.86,0:19:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,reveals that the gel-banas
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.11,0:19:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,have been torn apart at a molecular level.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.65,0:19:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So they turned into something that was no longer a banana.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's bad, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.12,0:19:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the only thing that comes to mind
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,is the EM-wave effect of the Phone Microwave (name subject to change).
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.12,0:19:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.38,0:19:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,My intuition as a mad scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.71,0:19:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,So, no reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, it's all set.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's use these.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.43,0:20:05.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't these Mayushii's?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.14,0:20:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I bought them with research funds Mayuri donated to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.43,0:20:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that make them hers—?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's toss the whole thing in and see the effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't just one work? Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.11,0:20:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we really uncover the Phone Microwave (name subject to change)'s true power
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.03,0:20:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.49,0:20:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That (name subject to change) thing is annoying. We should get rid of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.75,0:20:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't overhaul the world's ruling structure
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,if we're stingy with experimental funding!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.96,0:20:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the only one who wants to, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.30,0:20:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.60,0:20:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The banana's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.44,0:20:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.07,0:21:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Execute Emergency Order 666.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.86,0:21:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Initiate the cool-off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.91,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Government approval?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.12,0:21:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Talking to yourself... weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.41,0:21:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd you hide it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.20,0:21:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You're the one who hid it, Okarin.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.79,0:21:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This must be some kind of teleporter microwave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.38,0:21:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,How else do you explain this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We took the banana from the bunch, put it into the microwave, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Gel... bana...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.82,0:21:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's completely connected to the rest of the bunch...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.65,0:21:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,A second ago... We definitely removed one, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.62,0:21:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.03,0:21:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really a teleporter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's an interesting experiment you're conducting there, Okabe Rintarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.84,0:22:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Mr. Hououin Kyouma, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.80,0:22:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Makise Kurisu?
